name: I Have Infinite Skill Points
summary: Wang Lan's world is facing the threat of demon invasion and modern weapons are of no use. What humans can rely on are those who have awakened their Star Martial talent. Wang is one of the awakened and has a good helper. Maybe too good...“Successfully destroyed a Demon spy team, 100 thousand XP points and 5000 skill points rewarded.”“System, can you stop giving me points? I just want to focus on cultivation on my own.”“Nop, you don’t!”
author: East City Order
